<item>
            <title>[AMQ-2486] systemExitOnShutdown=&quot;true&quot; causes broker shutdown to hang</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-2486</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;To reproduce:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;add systemExitOnShutdown=&quot;true&quot; to the &amp;lt;broker&amp;gt; tag&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;start a broker&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;try to stop the broker&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12483055">AMQ-2486</key>
            <summary>systemExitOnShutdown=&quot;true&quot; causes broker shutdown to hang</summary>
